Package net.minestom.server.inventory

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EquipmentHandler
    Represents an Entity which can have ItemStack in hands and armor slots.
    InventoryClickHandler
    Represents an inventory which can receive click input.
    InventoryModifier
    Represents an inventory where items can be modified/retrieved.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Inventory
    Represents an inventory which can be viewed by a collection of Player.
    PlayerInventory
    Represents the inventory of a Player, retrieved with Player.getInventory().

    List of inventory property and their ID
